.bt
\fB&ta\fI|Nt|...\fR	0.8;|0.5in	none	E,\fBm\fR	Tab settings; \fIleft\fR type, unless \fIt=\fBR\fR(right), \fBC\fR(centered).
.b1
\fB&tc\fI|c\fR	none	none	E	Tab repetition character.
.b1
